{"tid":746613,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"奶共藝人係咁消費黃子華究竟係咩玩法","createTime":"2018-07-17T16:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-18T01:23:28.000Z","uid":56321,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"aa723d6927b9c1485931aaec4f8e4a15fea58e7f","tid":746613,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:26:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>【第十場棟篤笑】蘇永康全家捧子華神：你仍然狀態大勇</strong><br />\n<br />\n黃子華繼續在紅館演出棟篤笑，跟子華神私交甚篤的蘇永康（阿公），帶同老婆和囝囝Jazz捧場，不過由於個騷講明兒童不宜，就連子華神的契仔Jazz都冇得傾，只有早點入紅館跟契爺打招呼兼合照留念。<br />\n<br />\n阿公今晚在社交平台上載一家三口跟子華神合照，阿公說：「因為個Show講到明『兒童不宜』，所以契仔都無得傾，唯有早啲到紅館，契爺化妝整頭時Jazz可以周圍玩！一開Show守規矩地立即上車回家！ps：老友第十場你仍然狀態大勇！堅佩服👍👍 #thankful #enjoy #黃子華棟篤笑金盤𠺘口 #子華神 #佩服 #babisojazz」<br />\n<br />\n蘇永康帶同老婆和囝囝齊捧黃子華棟篤笑。（蘇永康instagram圖片/資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1531666255604&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1531666255604%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180715&d=kgcH8OIeiWSgf0BUAkWMp54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ec623ef5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz3.php%3Fnodeid%3D1531666255604%26subcate%3Dlatest%26issue%3D20180715&h=d64d1ce4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz3.php?nodeid=1531666255604&amp;subcate=latest&amp;issue=20180715</a>"},{"pid":"f901cd23967f34bd0dbd5119ed7bfa77444c177c","tid":746613,"uid":94454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:29:12.000Z","msg":"Clout chasing <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"322a15bf340089686048b3e736a19c2cb1818cc7","tid":746613,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"甚篤係咩意思"},{"pid":"4dab6f6b290a9be94137325f569835e4940a622f","tid":746613,"uid":56321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:33:10.000Z","msg":"黃子華一連26場的最後棟篤笑騷《黃子華棟篤笑金盆𠺘口》，今晚在紅館開鑼，場外設有紀念品售賣攤位，發售子華神對上一次棟篤笑騷《唔黐線唔正常》DVD，售價150元，及今次棟篤笑騷的100元「回水」杯，吸引數百粉絲「打蛇餅」排隊搶購。<br />\n<br />\n今晚全場爆滿，捧場圈中人眾多，包括<strong>劉嘉玲、黃秋生、吳鎮宇、黎耀祥、李嘉欣、白雪仙、陳寶珠、蔡一傑、關心妍、古巨基、施南生、林子善、曾勵珍、蘇施黃、金燕玲、蕭定一等</strong>。晚上8時10分準時開騷，先播出子華歷年棟篤笑片段長達15分鐘。隨著大會呼籲觀眾嚴禁盜錄偷影，子華於8時25分出場，台下即狂叫「回水」。子華爆金句：「回水無得傾，除褲太高清！大家有得叫好叫，都係你哋搞到我無得撈。」<br />\n<br />\n隨即講政治的子華說：「藝人要色盲，做黃絲無得撈，藍絲有孝心要瀨阿爺，24孝之最。」他更笑指最夠運當年考不到警察，現在做警察常被人問候伯母，笑言香港警察都是「母警」，又在台上爆粗，稱18歲以下不可入場。另外，之前黃牛黨炒高子華「收咪作」的票價，今晚卻要割價求售。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1259547/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1259547%2F&d=kgcH8OIeiWSgf0BUAkWMp54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7c87b3fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Flife%2Fent%2Frealtime%2F1259547%2F&h=9d7f31e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1259547/</a><br />\n<br />\n上面有幾個偽人應該比番張飛人哋啦，人笑你又笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25cc670e14eb34f0c7621ec606fcd03e4a5565a3","tid":746613,"uid":22465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"322a15bf340089686048b3e736a19c2cb1818cc7","tid":746613,"uid":70832,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T16:30:59.000Z","msg":"甚篤係咩意思"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:47:49.000Z","msg":"即係close既意思"},{"pid":"87833a7c114dc1492e5e2488e4726938ec6668fd","tid":746613,"uid":555,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:49:13.000Z","msg":"人地去睇下show都要比你班廢物批鬥"},{"pid":"75aece4ea2b5dfdc57e5cad18e819c8238672956","tid":746613,"uid":3454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T00:50:55.000Z","msg":"搵食啫 犯法呀?"},{"pid":"ed530eca91a7673f88bc2e9a17309f373d0dd454","tid":746613,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl